metadata.name: Burnout
metadata.description:
This artwork describes how an "Artist's Burnout" looks.  
Artist's Burnout is just part of your creative journey. Just because you are having Burnout doesn't mean that your creative life is over. It's just part of the process.  
The more you try to force your way out, The flames will get stronger.  
So at a time like this. Take it easy on yourself.
